19:54.294 --> 19:55.695
* My dad

19:56.529 --> 19:58.164
Yes! Come on, Dad!
You're doing it!

19:58.197 --> 20:01.234
Wow. I hate sushi.
I'm just realizing that.

20:01.268 --> 20:02.569
This is my dad!

20:02.602 --> 20:04.070
May I join you?

20:05.872 --> 20:06.906
You made it.

20:06.939 --> 20:08.308
Aw, it's the least
I could do.

20:09.476 --> 20:12.345
Oh, I'd like to propose
a Thanksgiving toast --

20:12.379 --> 20:14.247
to family.

20:14.281 --> 20:16.583
The ones
we're born with...

20:16.616 --> 20:18.451
the ones
we get to choose...

20:18.485 --> 20:20.853
the good ones
who step up day after day,

20:20.887 --> 20:23.222
no matter
what is asked of them.

20:24.391 --> 20:26.793
This is what love looks like,
people!

20:26.826 --> 20:29.696
This is what a father does
for his children.

20:29.729 --> 20:30.863
[ Clink ]

20:30.897 --> 20:32.399
You know what?

20:33.900 --> 20:36.403
It doesn't matter
that I can't finish this.

20:36.436 --> 20:39.238
What matters
is that I tried.

20:39.272 --> 20:40.239
Shall we?

20:40.273 --> 20:41.207
